title: Murder investigation launched following fire (The Metropolitan Police)
text: ( Source : The Metropolitan Police ) Detectives have launched a murder investigation following a fatal fire in Barnet . Police were called at 05:56hrs on Monday, 12 October , to reports of a fire at a ground floor flat in Finch Close , Barnet.
